data.description: Beautifully Upgraded 4 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom Home in the Sought-after Community of Rosetta Canyon!  Opportunity knocks with this well priced turnkey family home featuring Slab Granite, Glass Tile Backsplash, Stainless Steel Appliances, Vented Hood, Composite Sink, Birch Cabinets, Plank Vinyl Flooring (throughout), Downstairs Bed & Bathroom, Upgraded Bathrooms, Views from All upstairs rooms (single story homes on both sides), Professionally landscaped yard with Large Alummawood solid Patio Cover with fans/lights, Fully appointed Barbeque Island with under-counter lights, Additional Service Island, Cul de Sac Location, no homes behind and walking distance to the Community Sports Park makes this one a must see!
